         <abstract id="aspace_383535321e503511f1962b025f04e7a3">Incoming correspondence, including letters from Irving Berlin, Aaron Copland and others, and edited typescripts for the books, <title render="italic">
               <part>Eyes of Discovery</part>
            </title>,<title render="italic">
               <part>Spies of the Revolution</part>
            </title>, <title render="italic">
               <part>In the Big Time</part>
            </title>, <title render="italic">
               <part>Lewis and Clark, Partners in Discovery</part>
            </title>, and<title render="italic">
               <part>Daniel Boone: Master of the Wilderness</part>
            </title>.  Research materials, including copies of historical documents and photographs.The papers of Katherine Bakeless are also included in the collection.</abstract>
